vsParam:
Wow~ Verbena~!
We're here to have fun~!

Hey, everyone. Welcome.
What's your plan for today?
We want to hear it again!

Huh!?
Nooooo! Don't say stupid things!

Uh— We don't~!
It was indeed a great song!

Hmm, yeah...!
It's so romantic and sweet...!

Ha-ha-ha, of course it is~ This is a Love Song that
has been warmed by the heart for several hundred years~

Huh, several hundred years...?
I thought she created it on the spot.

Ha-ha-ha, how was that possible~ Can you produce
lyrics right when you are singing?

... Hmm, unlikely.
So it means... I get it.

The song she sang has been hiding
in her heart the whole time... I see.

Ha-ha-ha— Verbena is blushing~!
Isn't this nice~

The song that contains emotions harbored for several hundred
years... ♪ It got to be touching~

Hmm, stop saying that!
And... I'm getting angry!

Come, let me hear your Love Songs! At your age,
I'm sure you have had one or two love affairs, right!?

I-I didn't... I don't have a crush on...
Arrott!?

Me, me either. I haven't entered the workforce,
and I'm not interested in such things at all!!!

Hahaha... I... Hmm.
Love... is, quite hard...

Hehe, don't try to fool me.
I'll keep badgering you until all of you share your Love Songs!

Be quick about it!
Think about your feelings for the guy in your heart!

Eruleum is the place of hot hearts, of love and admiration...
which will never disappear!!

The Song of the Blue Sea, the Song of Love
                                                                          —THE END—
